           if        w-det-prt-mag-inx    >    w-det-prt-mag-max
                     go to acc-prt-bfo-mag-040.
           move      zero                 to   w-det-prt-mag-prt
                                              (w-det-prt-mag-inx)
                                               w-det-prt-mag-drg
                                              (w-det-prt-mag-inx)     .
           go to     acc-prt-bfo-mag-020.
       acc-prt-bfo-mag-040.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
