      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rr-prt-bfo           to   w-wrk-nos-acc          .
           move      w-wrk-num-saa        to   w-wrk-noc-saa          .
           move      01                   to   w-wrk-noc-dpz          .
           move      w-wrk-num-npg        to   w-wrk-noc-npg          .
           move      w-wrk-nos-int        to   w-det-prt-mag-prw      .
       acc-prt-bfo-mag-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test preliminari                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
