           if        w-det-prt-mag-ctr    >    w-det-prt-mag-max
                     move  w-det-prt-mag-max
                                          to   w-det-prt-mag-ctr      .
           move      rf-bfs-prt-mag       to   w-det-prt-mag-prt
                                              (w-det-prt-mag-ctr)     .
           move      rf-bfs-drg-mag       to   w-det-prt-mag-drg
                                              (w-det-prt-mag-ctr)     .
       acc-prt-bfo-mag-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a record successivo                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-prt-bfo-mag-200.
       acc-prt-bfo-mag-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-prt-bfo-mag-999.
       acc-prt-bfo-mag-999.
           exit.

